{"tid":1275620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 7.1 發生嘅唔係暴力行為 - 係 官逼民反","createTime":"2019-07-01T21:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T23:07:06.000Z","uid":64918,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7f218be6ad3b4bf62020f44c4cda8baa53d37783","tid":1275620,"uid":64918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:02:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>官逼民反 </strong><br />\n<br />\n到底&quot;撤回&quot; 呢兩個字有幾難 ? <br />\n已經有三個人死咗, <strong>唔應該指責被壓迫既人 應該指責壓迫人果個人</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/H93D3R0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH93D3R0.jpg&h=5c2d9cae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日朝頭早嗰3段說話 <br />\n<br />\n//毛孟靜：「你哋衝入去，係會當成暴動，要坐十年㗎！入面仲要準備晒槍等你哋㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n有人回答：「預咗啦！已經有三個人死咗啦！我哋預咗啦！」//<br />\n<br />\n//睇直播見到幾個議員頂住㗎車唔畀人撞入去，啲𡃁仔講「你畀我哋撞入去啦！我預咗比人拉㗎啦！你仲想我哋等幾耐呀？仲有乜嘢方法呀」//<br />\n<br />\n//有社總朋友/教友說:<br />\n在現場的社工朋友透露，他們不是鬼，而係死士，有十幾人，預了無咗條命。另一朋友也說，現場青少年告昨晚煲底開會，有九人舉手做死士<br />\n所以佢哋係想自殺，不過用另一方式。//<br />\n<br />\n啲人唔係有暴力傾向, 相反佢哋係有 <strong><strong>犧牲</strong></strong> 傾向. 對政府係完全失望, 甚至乎感到絕望.  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0375JSA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0375JSA.png&h=27ba69ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有句說話叫 冰封三尺非一日之寒 ,"},{"pid":"0ef13797492fa6a9d614b9d7b9e2411e5d738bb7","tid":1275620,"uid":18730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:05:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59af15ee2bcbfe954029d6cf80eff8ad56a3022e","tid":1275620,"uid":64918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:11:13.000Z","msg":"官逼民反, 將會係聽日 ( 今日 ) 輿論最重要嘅四個字. 亦都希望 傳媒朋友 同埋文宣 唔好俾人將今日嘅行動俾人抹黑. <br />\n<br />\n會有好多中間 市民唔明白點解會用暴力, 但係我哋至少要令到佢哋 諗 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>雖然我未必贊同佢地做法 但我支持示威者</strong>"},{"pid":"0495ef18774197305b0e9b8ed91b2f66d12ba5a9","tid":1275620,"uid":64918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:17:45.000Z","msg":"仲有另外一樣 比較複雜啲嘅 Concept... 我諗要大家諗下有咩辦法容易啲翻譯.<br />\n<br />\n開口埋口法治, Rule Of Law, 但係其實英文還有一個字叫 rule by law。Rule by law就是只根據法律來治理就成，即使那條法律是苛刻或殘酷的。英文有分rule of law和rule by law，但中文兩個都是叫「法治」。"},{"pid":"b2fd0b3766468ebb66b5272e16e5f1377c98c782","tid":1275620,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edb45d6b08c4ea1b93fa2284b8d46bda181c6a5","tid":1275620,"uid":228181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:19:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb7cc52b582e045faa15473b7bc39182633b72d","tid":1275620,"uid":64918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6edb45d6b08c4ea1b93fa2284b8d46bda181c6a5","tid":1275620,"uid":228181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:19:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d7ae8a9db99ab68ec5178780a70511a1446874","tid":1275620,"uid":127532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:27:23.000Z","msg":"唔明點解打爆玻璃，塗鴉，佔領係暴力<br />\n又唔係打人，最多咪毀壞公物"},{"pid":"e8a010c0e03f1448a5c3beb5408bdc381a1dc209","tid":1275620,"uid":64918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:37:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cdb7c7620a2ded1e66133993cd08589a3919c45a","tid":1275620,"uid":