寒 ,"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:19:56.000Z","msg":"無論今日你覺得啱定錯，無論你係勇武定係和理非，<br />\n我哋互補長短，絕不分化，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要怪就怪問題嘅本身，香港政府，漠視民意22年！官逼民反！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無論你和理非定係勇武，只要理念一致，大於一切！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從來製造社會動亂只有當權者，並非反抗者！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋絕不分化！不篤灰！不割蓆！不流血！不被捕！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人企返埋一齊！"},{"pid":"1488195478a721d3059f9147e885dc0a46fb5f5b","tid":1275620,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:20:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3aa0484ea71a390d7516ceb1963f8b8db4d6a7ef","tid":1275620,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:20:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">得閒唔該幫手推一下 推到義士起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【廣傳】所有出現過喺現場嘅義士，見到呢個post 即刻更改Facebook私隱設定，尤其係相！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275626</a></span>"},{"pid":"9a9cf98bc1127cc91a0f6593ccba52883992c91a","tid":1275620,"uid":64918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:23:41.000Z","msg":"今日所有國際新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMXQVvn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMXQVvn.jpg&h=4884035c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對住廢老就唔好用, 外國嘅報道係, 點解政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔回應</strong></span>民意."},{"pid":"22cbcbe2ded1125963a550cddb24d65a9f16cfa3","tid":1275620,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:23:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8d9123d39ff19941217601326db197d811d2620e","tid":1275620,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:24:37.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"12f44cc6f65bbbca9250383df4a1845a653fab0a","tid":1275620,"ui